Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.10,0:19:55.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,咦诶诶~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:58.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,只有飞过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.67,0:20:03.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,我先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:06.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？春香你要先过去？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.13,0:20:09.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,等等嘛 别丢下我一个人
